import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Switch, Route, Redirect, Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from './home'


export default (
  <BrowserRouter>
    <Switch id='routes'>
      <Route exact path='/' render={ () =>   <Home /> }/>
      <Route path='/home' component={ () => <Home /> }/>

    </Switch>
  </BrowserRouter>
)
